Package: scRNAimputeR
Title: Collection of scRNAseq Imputation Algorithms
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Miles",
           family = "Smith",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mileschristiansmith@gmail.com")
Description: Collects scRNAseq imputation algorithms and 
    provides functions for interfacing with Seurat and 
    SingleCellExperiment objects.
